resources.string: This is a CardView widget. CardView widgets can have shadows and rounded corners. \\n\\nTo create a card with a shadow, use the <font fgcolor=\"#FFFFFFFF\">android:elevation</font> attribute. \\n\\nTo set the corner radius in your layouts, use the <font fgcolor=\"#FFFFFFFF\">card_view:cardCornerRadius</font> attribute.
